OL,3,CJersey's Appointment of Ministers -
OL,4,Cfollow live
OL,6,FJersey's new States Members are
OL,7,Fmeeting to choose the next Council of
OL,8,FMinisters.
OL,10,FChief Minister Designate, Senator
OL,11,FLyndon Farnham, has already proposed
OL,12,Fhis ministerial selections.
OL,14,FHowever, States Members will now have
OL,15,Fthe opportunity to nominate their own
OL,16,Fpreferred candidates for each
OL,17,FMinisterial role.
OL,19,FThe Ministerial roles being elected
OL,20,Fare:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
