OL,3,CJersey's Appointment of Ministers -
OL,4,Cfollow live
OL,6,F11:10: Senator Elaine Millar nominated
OL,7,Ffor Minister for Social Security
OL,9,FSenator Millar, who served as Treasury
OL,10,FMinister in the last political term,
OL,11,Fhas been selected as Senator Farnham's
OL,12,Fpreferred choice for Social Security
OL,13,FMinister.
OL,15,FIn her opening speech, Senator Millar
OL,16,Fsays one of her priorities is
OL,17,Fintroducing a secondary pension scheme
OL,18,Fand supporting those with childcare
OL,19,Fcosts.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
