OL,3,CJersey's Appointment of Ministers -
OL,4,Cfollow live
OL,6,F11:10: IAN GORST ELECTED AS EXTERNAL
OL,7,FAFFAIRS MINISTER
OL,9,FFollowing a flurry of questions,
OL,10,FSenator Ian Gorst has been elected
OL,11,Finto the position in which he held in
OL,12,Fthe last political term - External
OL,13,FAffairs Minister.
OL,15,F10:40: Ian Gorst nominated for
OL,16,FExternal Affairs
OL,18,FOnto our third election of the day and
OL,19,FSenator Ian Gorst is on his feet
OL,20,Fmaking his pitch to colleagues.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
