OL,3,CJersey's Appointment of Ministers -
OL,4,Cfollow live
OL,6,FSenator Gorst says he will do his
OL,7,Futmost to strengthen ties with the
OL,8,FUnited Kingdom, especially now with 'a
OL,9,Fnew Prime Minister soon in place.'
OL,11,FHe says he wants to continue to see
OL,12,FJersey's voice heard with the effects
OL,13,Fof Brexit being felt.
OL,15,F10:38: HELEN MILES ELECTED AS JUSTICE
OL,16,FAND HOME AFFAIRS MINISTER
OL,18,FTwo out of two so far for Senator
OL,19,FFarnham as Senator Miles is elected
OL,20,Finto the position for Minister for
OL,21,FJustice and Home Affairs.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
