OL,3,CJersey's Appointment of Ministers -
OL,4,Cfollow live
OL,6,F10:23: Miles talks immigration
OL,8,FFollowing a question from Deputy
OL,9,FKirsten Morel around immigration laws,
OL,10,FSenator Miles says she would like to
OL,11,Fsee the introduction of an Immigration
OL,12,FLaw which could look at the
OL,13,F'controllables' within Jersey's
OL,14,Fpolitical system.
OL,16,FIt's worth noting that, given Jersey
OL,17,Fis part of the Common Travel Area,
OL,18,Frules around immigration mainly fall
OL,19,Fwithin UK legislation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/11
