OL,3,CJersey's Appointment of Ministers -
OL,4,Cfollow live
OL,6,F10:13: Senator Helen Miles nominated
OL,7,Ffor Minister for Justice and Home
OL,8,FAffairs
OL,10,FThe poll topper at this month's
OL,11,Felection, Senator Helen Miles, has
OL,12,Fbeen nominated for the position of
OL,13,FJustice and Home Affairs Minister.
OL,15,FShe was tipped to stand for the top
OL,16,Fjob but stood aside for Senator
OL,17,FFarnham.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
