OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1782839908
OL,3,CJersey's Appointment of Ministers -
OL,4,Cfollow live
OL,6,FIn her speech, she talks of continuing
OL,7,Fto instill 'public confidence' but
OL,8,Falso wants more 'victims to be heard'
OL,9,Fand 'supporting vulnerable adults'
OL,11,FShe says she wants to continue to
OL,12,Fchampion the things that people don't
OL,13,Fsee within public protection.
OL,15,F10:06: TOM BINET ELECTED AS HEALTH
OL,16,FMINISTER
OL,18,FSenator Tom Binet has been re-elected
OL,19,Fas Health Minister - the only person
OL,20,Fto stand for the job.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
