OL,3,CJersey's Appointment of Ministers -
OL,4,Cfollow live
OL,6,F9.54: Senator Binet taking questions
OL,8,FWhilst Senator Binet takes questions,
OL,9,Fit might be worth explaining what we
OL,10,Fmight see over the course of the day.
OL,12,FSenator Farnham may well see
OL,13,Fchallenges to his nominations
OL,14,Fincluding for Infrastructure and
OL,15,FSustainable Economic Development.
OL,17,FHowever, it's unclear who exactly will
OL,18,Fbe the challengers.
OL,20,F9:47: A warm response
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/11
