OL,3,CJersey's Appointment of Ministers -
OL,4,Cfollow live
OL,6,FSenator Binet got a rapturous stamping
OL,7,Fof feet following his speech - now
OL,8,Fit's onto the questions.
OL,10,FIn another note, the Bailiff has noted
OL,11,Fthe Chamber is particularly stuffy
OL,12,Ftoday - a hangover from the extreme
OL,13,Fweather we have had over the past week.
OL,15,FPoliticians have been permitted to
OL,16,Fremove jackets if needed.
OL,18,F9:38: Senator Tom Binet nominated
OL,19,Funcontested as Health Minister
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
