PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1782839908
OL,3,CJersey's Appointment of Ministers -
OL,4,Cfollow live
OL,6,FIt is an unsurprising start to
OL,7,Fproceedings as Senator Binet will
OL,8,Fagain become the Minister for Health
OL,9,Fand Social Services.
OL,11,FSenator Binet was the Health Minister
OL,12,Ffor the last political term, and was
OL,13,Fone of three incumbent ministerial
OL,14,Fselections Senator Farnham put forward.
OL,16,FSenator Binet says in his speech that
OL,17,Fdigitisation will bring Jersey out of
OL,18,Fthe "Dickensian Age".
OL,20,F09:30 : Meeting set to begin
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
