PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1782839908
OL,3,CJersey's Appointment of Ministers -
OL,4,Cfollow live
OL,6,FThe States Members have arrived and
OL,7,Fare currently being roll-called.
OL,9,FFirstly, candidates will be put
OL,10,Fforward for each ministerial role.
OL,12,FEach candidate will give a speech for
OL,13,Fup to 10 minutes and answer questions
OL,14,Ffrom the Assembly for up to 20 minutes
OL,15,Fbefore the Assembly votes.
OL,17,FWhile they do so, other candidates
OL,18,Fwill have to leave the Chamber, as
OL,19,Fthey cannot be present during another
OL,20,Fspeech
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/11
